# 腾讯优量汇 - 广告服务商
DOMAIN, ios.bugly.qq.com, REJECT
DOMAIN, sdk.e.qq.com, REJECT
DOMAIN, us.l.qq.com, REJECT
DOMAIN-SUFFIX, ugdtimg.com, REJECT
